      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/e52b6/anpai.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"anpai\"\n        title=\"anpai\"\n        src=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/e52b6/anpai.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/a80bd/anpai.jpg 148w,\n/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/1c91a/anpai.jpg 295w,\n/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/e52b6/anpai.jpg 390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 390px) 100vw, 390px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>具体实现方式就是利用 html2canvas 对一个 Div 进行截图，在这个 Div 里有记仇的图片和可编辑的文本框，然后再在下面展示并下载下来就阔以了，这部分涉及到了 base64 图片的下载，也是借用了 segmentFault 上 <a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/q/1010000005816241\">大神的代码</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/MLuminary/subentry/tree/master/%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%87%E5%85%88%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5\">项目地址</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"今天这个仇先记下来","date":"May 18, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/今天这个仇先记下来/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/跨域问题总结/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"跨域问题总结","date":"2018-05-19 22:45:37"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/性感慕课在线被爬/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"性感慕课在线被爬","date":"2018-05-02 21:09:47"}},"prePath":"/posts/post-1526741137000","nextPath":"/posts/post-1525266587000"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1747850863","63159454"]}